{"tid":2452672,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（崇美的中國人）阿凡達中國大陸重新上畫 3天票房衝破15億元","createTime":"2021-03-19T03:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T15:53:24.000Z","uid":66087,"like":118,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"af0f74562d41d5df50b32ce1f4d9504eac2c82c8","tid":2452672,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:38:38.000Z","msg":"國際 | 財經<br />\n<br />\n即時新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhbgDAx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhbgDAx.jpg&h=58df6fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國科幻電影「阿凡達」（Avatar）昨天在中國大陸重新上映再奪票房冠軍，今天累計票房已經超越「復仇者聯盟：終局之戰」（Avengers: Endgame），重返全球電影票房冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n美國科幻電影《阿凡達》時隔11年後在中國大陸重新上映，此次重映包括普通3D和IMAX3D兩個版本，上映三天就高達人民幣15億元大關，加上11年前累積金額，已重新登上全球影史單片票房冠軍寶座，擠下復仇者聯盟4。"},{"pid":"956ad5ce1b6649d177813a2752c5ab3daf57407d","tid":2452672,"uid":66087,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"原來中國人的錢真易賺，美國今次fat fat 了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcb840fb2db51e4bcecf70fe671da8e7438ad1f","tid":2452672,"uid":76793,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"當年無睇過3d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇返"},{"pid":"6bc7aff16cbadb6a0b117ac1e3849f6368632465","tid":2452672,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6950d5a03ae0af54442cec57d1b56ba67491369e","tid":2452672,"uid":324629,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"阿凡達過左10年有多，仲係咁好賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f